ActVictims Bill of Rights Act
SubjectOrder Fixing July 23, 2015 as the Day on which Certain Provisions of the Victims Bill of Rights Act Come into Force
PrecisOrder fixing July 23, 2015 as the coming into force date (1) of paragraph 26(1)(c) of the CORRECTIONS AND CONDITIONAL RELEASE ACT, as enacted by subsection 46(3) of the Victims Bill of Righst Act; and (2) of section 45, subsections 46(2) and 46(4) to (7), section 47, subsections 48(1) and (2) and 49(2) and sections 50 and 51 of the VICTIMS BILL OF RIGHTS ACT, chapter 13 of the Statutes of Canada, 2015.
